    "## 1.4 What This Book Will Teach You\n",
    "\n",
    "This book focuses on three major themes:\n",
    "\n",
    "### **1. TensorFlow Fundamentals**\n",
    "- Execution styles (eager mode & graphs)\n",
    "- Core components: `tf.Variable`, `tf.Tensor`, operations\n",
    "- Model-building APIs in Keras\n",
    "- Scalable and efficient data ingestion pipelines\n",
    "\n",
    "### **2. Deep Learning Algorithms**\n",
    "- Fully connected networks (FCNs)\n",
    "- Convolutional neural networks (CNNs)\n",
    "- Recurrent neural networks (RNNs)\n",
    "- Transformer architectures\n",
    "\n",
    "### **3. Monitoring & Optimization**\n",
    "- Using TensorBoard for tracking and visualization\n",
    "- Understanding model behavior through explainability tools\n",
    "- Improving training speed and performance\n",
