    "## Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "Chapter 1 establishes the foundation for understanding TensorFlow's role in machine learning:\n",
    "\n",
    "- TensorFlow provides a powerful ecosystem for building deep learning models efficiently.\n",
    "- It excels when handling large datasets, complex architectures, and production pipelines.\n",
    "- GPUs significantly boost TensorFlow’s performance, especially for deep neural networks.\n",
    "- TensorFlow is not always suitable for traditional ML tasks or small-scale data.\n",
